00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:34,630
Good!

248
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:38,570
Very good!

249
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:47,690
♫ The continuous rain and rustling wind ♫

250
00:19:47,690 --> 00:19:51,100
♫ Stirred thousands layers of waves ♫

251
00:19:51,100 --> 00:19:58,040
♫ Flowing, flowing to tranquility ♫

252
00:19:58,040 --> 00:20:04,640
♫ This blizzard, it’s witnessed my journey ♫

253
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,720
Move out of the way!

254
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:09,340
Master, Guo Youdao once said,

255
00:20:09,340 --> 00:20:11,700
it doesn't matter what happened in the past,

256
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:17,660
we have to continue moving forward.

257
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:21,990
Don't look back!

258
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:34,840
♫ Every teardrop is a star ♫

259
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:54,120
That direction is the Big Dipper Academy.

260
00:20:55,620 --> 00:20:57,580
It has been 19 years already.

261
00:20:57,580 --> 00:20:59,980
It feels like a dream.

262
00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:04,179
Master, that's all in the past.

263
00:21:04,179 --> 00:21:06,600
Don't worry about it!

264
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:08,600
How's the teacher?

265
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:15,159
Chief Yan Jin seems hurt.

266
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:18,180
He needs some time to recover.

267
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:22,219
- Take me to have a look.
- Yes.

268
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:31,360
Master.

269
00:21:33,860 --> 00:21:36,360
What are you doing?

270
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:38,560
The Mountain and Sea Gang doesn't tolerate failure.

271
00:21:38,560 --> 00:21:42,060
This is the punishment demanded by Chief Yan Jin himself.

272
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:44,850
- Get lost!
- Yes.

273
00:21:44,850 --> 00:21:49,840
[Sea and Mountain View]

274
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:07,020
Why did Teacher do that?

275
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:09,970
I acted recklessly this time.

276
00:22:09,970 --> 00:22:12,400
I'm the one to blame.

277
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:16,260
Please punish me, Master.

278
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:21,720
Your guqin was already broken.

279
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,959
I bought you a new one.

280
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,980
The surface is made of Candlenut wood and the bottom is Catalpa.

281
00:22:25,980 --> 00:22:27,980
They are the best materials.

282
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:31,880
I also made a secret compartment for you to hide weapons.

283
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:36,340
Master, all these years, I have been here for you,

284
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:39,760
hoping to hide your identity and keep you safe.

285
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:42,940
You should not take risks for my life.

286
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:47,120
Moreover, you should not be merciful to me, either.

287
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:49,260
Did you forget?

288
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:53,800
Weakness can make people lose their fighting spirit.

289
00:22:53,800 --> 00:22:55,580
Teacher,

290
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:58,300
you are wrong.

291
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:05,280
Anyone can be sacrificed, except you.

292
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:08,400
It's because I remember.

293
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,700
Back then, when I was seriously injured and lost my mind,

294
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:14,060
it was only you who didn't want to give up and saved me.

295
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:18,639
Others advised me to live on with my injuries.

296
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:23,980
You were the only one who made me face myself in the mirror.

297
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:28,080
Look!

298
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:31,300
Take a good look at yourself!

299
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:37,299
Look at yourself!

300
00:23:37,299 --> 00:23:39,180
Look!

301
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:14,430
You told me that if I wanted to achieve something big,

302
00:24:14,430 --> 00:24:16,880
I must do it at all cost,

303
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:21,920
I need to do it myself, and be extremely cruel and merciless.

304
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:27,020
It was you who picked me up from a pile of dirt and cheered me on.

305
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:29,710
You're like a mirror to me,

306
00:24:29,710 --> 00:24:34,220
showing me my scars and my hatred.

307
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:38,300
Teacher, can I still leave you?

308
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:52,840
Your Majesty.

309
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:58,860
You were confused.

310
00:24:58,860 --> 00:25:02,040
How can there still be any king and his ministers?

311
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:04,740
Ever since the fire at the Seven Martyr Court,

312
00:25:04,740 --> 00:25:07,360
the prince has already died.

313
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:12,900
I'm not afraid of being recognized by others.

314
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:16,040
I'm also not the Liu Song from before.

315
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:21,940
Take good care of yourself!

316
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:24,240
What happens moving forward,

317
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:26,380
I'll take care of it.

318
00:25:34,560 --> 00:25:36,790
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

319
00:25:36,790 --> 00:25:40,620
Everyone, former disciple of the Big Dipper, Liu Song,

320
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:43,160
has been controlling the Mountain and Sea Gang for many years.

321
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:46,959
He has caused a lot of troubles and killed many martial art masters.

322
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:51,239
He wanted to start a war and bring disaster to the common people.

323
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:54,260
Since this is the right thing to do,

324
00:25:54,260 --> 00:25:57,620
the Big Dipper should stand up

325
00:25:57,620 --> 00:26:00,160
and clean up our sect.

326
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:04,799
Today, the Big Dipper has decided to ally itself with the Wuji Manor

327
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:07,039
to hold a Seven Star Convention.

328
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:09,190
We'll invite all sects in the martial arts circles

329
00:26:09,190 --> 00:26:12,610
to discuss the strategy of exterminating the Mountain and Sea Gang.

330
00:26:12,619 --> 00:26:15,160
I will personally draft the Seven Star Invitation

331
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:19,080
and have the disciples of each institute to deliver the invitations.

332
00:26:20,020 --> 00:26:24,379
As for the north of the Central Plains, Wuji Manor will issue the Master's order to summon other sects.

333
00:26:24,379 --> 00:26:28,039
Everyone, it's better to go according to the distance of your hometown.

334
00:26:28,039 --> 00:26:31,139
- Lin Feng, you will towards Jiangnan.
- Yes.

335
00:26:31,139 --> 00:26:34,119
- Li Jian, head towards the West.
- Yes.

336
00:26:34,119 --> 00:26:38,360
- Wei Tianqi, go towards Kaifeng.
- Yes.

337
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:41,999
That's great! I can finally meet Sangsang.

338
00:26:41,999 --> 00:26:45,920
Pavilion Master, please just let me go to Kaifeng.

339
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:51,099
- You… Lu Ping, why are you always fighting with me?
- Then you have to win against me.

340
00:26:51,099 --> 00:26:53,960
- You…
- This time, it's for serious business.

341
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:55,979
You can run an errand next time.

342
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:02,879
Pavilion Master, although it's a matter of the puglist world,

343
00:27:02,879 --> 00:27:04,999
but Liu Song is from the royal family of Dan.

344
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:07,960
I want to personally tell General Qin.

345
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:11,120
That's fine! Just let you to go to Kaifeng then.

346
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:12,980
Come back soon!

347
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:14,780
Thank you, Pavilion Master.

348
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:22,400
Master Guo, I have a personal request for you.

349
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:41,220
What do you want?

350
00:27:41,220 --> 00:27:45,820
I want to go to your Seven Martyr Court to get a good sword.

351
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:54,680
If you can get it,

352
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,560
then get it yourself.

353
00:27:58,200 --> 00:28:01,259
Master, why didn't you give me a weapon?

354
00:28:01,259 --> 00:28:03,580
You always give Lu Ping gifts.

355
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:07,900
Lu Ping, what do you do want with a sword?

356
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:12,820
Sangsang's sword is already broken. You want to—

357
00:28:12,820 --> 00:28:16,820
Get one if you can!

358
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:18,560
I will.

359
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:28,799
Master Guo, I still have one more thing to trouble you with.

360
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:34,059
My younger sister, she is obedient and sensible,

361
00:28:34,059 --> 00:28:37,560
but she was wronged a few days ago and is in a bad mood.

362
00:28:37,560 --> 00:28:41,880
Since you look like my master, when I'm away,

363
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:44,800
please take care of her.

364
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:47,380
Don't push your luck!

365
00:28:47,380 --> 00:28:49,910
I am not Guo Youdao.

366
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:53,040
You still are not as good as our master.

367
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:54,960
Who told you that?

368
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:57,400
If I want to, I can also take good care of her.

369
00:28:57,400 --> 00:29:00,480
Then thank you, Master.

370
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:05,380
How is your Master Chu Min

371
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:08,220
doing right now?

372
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:12,560
She is fine but Tang Xiaomei has been driven crazy.

373
00:29:26,980 --> 00:29:28,999
It's better for Lu Ping to go crazy instead of Master.

374
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,639
At least, Lu Ping lets me do the cleaning.

375
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:34,879
Master said if I come in the room to clean, she'll kill me with just a slap of her hand.

376
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:37,239
If she wants to go crazy, then she should drink inside her room.

377
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:39,060
What is she doing at the Fifth Institute?

378
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:43,360
Xiao Bai, it's not our fault that there are few people in our Fifth Institute.

379
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:45,620
This is the perfect place to go crazy.

380
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:51,120
Brother.

381
00:29:54,500 --> 00:29:56,680
After I leave,

382
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:59,540
I will hand over Master Chu Min to the two of you.

383
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:01,439
Give her 20 jars of wine each day.

384
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:03,079
Even if she smashes the jars, it's enough.

385
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:07,579
Brother, are you sure you won't try to persuade Master Chu Min anymore?

386
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:11,880
It's not easy to forget someone

387
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:15,040
who you've been remembering for over ten years.

388
00:30:16,860 --> 00:30:18,860
Just give her some time.

389
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:23,779
You are good at finding excuse for others, what about yourself?

390
00:30:23,779 --> 00:30:27,600
Mo Lin, how about only Su Tang continues living here?

391
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:30,900
I'll send you to the Seven Martyr Court so you can stay with Master Guo.

392
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:34,539
Boss, just pretend I didn't say anything.

393
00:30:34,539 --> 00:30:36,590
It's just because I keep seeing you and Eldest Senior fight—

394
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:38,210
Don't mention him!

395
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,840
I feel annoyed whenever he's brought up.

396
00:30:41,950 --> 00:30:43,550
I'm leaving.

397
00:30:49,570 --> 00:30:52,210
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

398
00:31:05,320 --> 00:31:08,620
You have so much free time to see me off?

399
00:31:08,620 --> 00:31:11,180
I heard you were going to send out Seven Star invitations.

400
00:31:11,180 --> 00:31:12,959
Liu Song is also in hiding right now.

401
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:15,260
We don't even know what he is plotting behind the scenes.

402
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:17,559
It's dangerous for you to go out in public alone.

403
00:31:17,560 --> 00:31:21,100
I can ask my father to send Ah Ze to go with you.

404
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:23,540
What do you mean by that?

405
00:31:23,540 --> 00:31:26,080
I'm so weak that I can't leave the mountain by myself, is that it?

406
00:31:26,080 --> 00:31:27,680
Don't you be bothered!

407
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:32,439
- Lu Ping, can't you just listen to me once?
- You are like this, just making me feel very useless.

408
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,960
Lu Ping.

409
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:39,580
Don't think that I dare not beat you.

410
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:45,180
I can't stand your protection.

411
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:36,040
The wind is cold and you've just recovered from injury.

412
00:32:36,040 --> 00:32:38,340
You still should pay more attention to your health.

413
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:41,740
Thank you for your concern.

414
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:44,880
Actually, you don't need to worry.

415
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:47,159
Young Lord Lu is just angry with you at the moment.

416
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:50,920
He will definitely understand you someday.

417
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:59,080
No matter where I am in the future, I will be happy for you.

418
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,800
Where are you going?

419
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:05,360
I am not a disciple of the Big Dipper.

420
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:07,600
I also don't want to depend on others.

421
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:10,340
Although I can't go back to Kaifeng right now,

422
00:33:10,340 --> 00:33:15,100
there must be a place for me in the pugilist world.

423
00:33:15,100 --> 00:33:19,040
I am here this time to say goodbye.

424
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:23,219
However, you are just a weak girl so how are you going to survive?

425
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:33,720
Performing or working, I will find a way to live.

426
00:33:35,060 --> 00:33:37,600
You don't have to worry.

427
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:42,560
I was a servant since childhood so I have already gotten used to these hardships.

428
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:47,080
It's my honor to meet you. Please take care!

429
00:33:51,460 --> 00:33:53,660
Goodbye!

430
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:05,960
Miss Ling, although Wuji Manor is located at the border,

431
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:08,280
at least, we still own a business.

432
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:12,180
If you don't mind, you can come with me.

433
00:34:12,180 --> 00:34:15,360
At least, you'll have a place to stay.

434
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:39,939
Stop feeding me! I want to go out and take a walk.

435
00:34:39,939 --> 00:34:43,130
General has ordered us to let you rest.

436
00:34:43,130 --> 00:34:46,400
General was injured before and got out of bed in just three days.

437
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:48,599
He even said he was fine as long as he's not bleeding.

438
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:51,659
Besides, more activity helps to recover muscles and bones.

439
00:34:51,659 --> 00:34:53,400
Miss.

440
00:34:53,860 --> 00:34:56,960
I'll be bored to death if I don't go out for a walk.

441
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:06,699
- General, is everything alright?
- Everything's fine.

442
00:35:06,699 --> 00:35:08,800
Should I find a blacksmith?

443
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:12,480
What do you know? The body of the Kuiying Sword is very thin.

444
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:14,540
If you find a blacksmith who casually messes with it,

445
00:35:14,540 --> 00:35:17,740
it will affect the exertion of Pneuma of Energy.

446
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:20,300
I never knew forging a sword was so...

447
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:23,680
Brother, what are you doing?

448
00:35:23,680 --> 00:35:28,660
Sang'er, this sword is your favorite.

449
00:35:28,660 --> 00:35:31,580
I originally wanted to fix it for you before giving it to you,

450
00:35:31,580 --> 00:35:35,580
but I didn't expect that I'm not good at forging swords.

451
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:43,980
As long as I was able to save my brother, who cares about the sword.

452
00:35:47,520 --> 00:35:50,959
Why are you still here? Take it back inside!

453
00:35:50,959 --> 00:35:53,559
- Hurry!
- Yes.

454
00:36:00,180 --> 00:36:03,579
Brother, I haven't seen you like this for a long time.

455
00:36:03,579 --> 00:36:07,140
You are not the scowling general but more like a black-faced brother. (TN: scowling and black-faced are homonyms).

456
00:36:07,140 --> 00:36:08,860
Don't get yourself dirty!

457
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:16,480
Actually, I feel very guilty seeing you hurt this time.

458
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:19,919
Brother, look at me! I am fine now.

459
00:36:19,919 --> 00:36:23,119
- I am alive and well.
- Okay. Okay.

460
00:36:23,119 --> 00:36:26,359
You just recovered. Don't get hurt again.

461
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:33,740
Sang'er, promise me!

462
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:36,599
Don't be so reckless from now on.

463
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:39,539
Don't rush forward with no regards to your life when you come across anything.

464
00:36:39,539 --> 00:36:43,899
I usually scold and lecture you, but it's all for your safety.

465
00:36:43,899 --> 00:36:45,960
Do you know?

466
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:49,450
When I saw you lying there with your face so white this time,

467
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:52,660
I really felt guilty.

468
00:36:55,760 --> 00:37:00,260
Brother, if you really regret not treating me well,

469
00:37:00,260 --> 00:37:02,700
then let me out for a walk.

470
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:05,079
I have almost recovered completely.

471
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:07,040
I want to move around.

472
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,699
Lu Ping has already gone back to the Big Dipper.

473
00:37:10,699 --> 00:37:13,120
You can't meet him here.

474
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:15,339
- But Brother—
- Sang'er,

475
00:37:15,339 --> 00:37:19,220
I am very grateful for all that Lu Ping has done in Yuezhou this time,

476
00:37:19,220 --> 00:37:22,190
but it doesn't mean I agree with the two of you being together.

477
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:27,220
- Why?
- You must remember that you are a daughter from a noble family.

478
00:37:27,220 --> 00:37:29,740
Your every word and action is under people's scrutiny.

479
00:37:29,740 --> 00:37:33,159
Besides, the Mountain and Sea Gang is now involved in politics.

480
00:37:33,160 --> 00:37:34,979
The identity of Lu Ping is sensitive.

481
00:37:34,979 --> 00:37:37,960
I don't want you to be involved in this chaotic situation

482
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:42,980
but I promise you that I will recommend Lu Ping to His Majesty.

483
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:46,359
If he gets an official position and works hard,

484
00:37:46,359 --> 00:37:49,760
then I won't stop your relationship at that time.

485
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,880
However, he already stated before

486
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:55,780
that he wanted to be an ordinary man who plants flowers in the countryside.

487
00:37:57,100 --> 00:38:02,059
He doesn't care about fame and wealth at all so how can he be an official?

488
00:38:02,059 --> 00:38:07,040
Then this is the perfect opportunity to see whether or not he will change for you.

489
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:17,320
Sang'er, you're the daughter of the Qin Family.

490
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:19,540
You're my beloved sister.

491
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:21,950
I don't want to see you suffer at all.

492
00:38:21,959 --> 00:38:26,020
Think about what I've just said.

493
00:38:26,020 --> 00:38:27,800
Okay?

494
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:40,060
How long have we been back from Yuezhou?

495
00:38:40,060 --> 00:38:45,140
Including the time that you've been recovering, it has been almost a month.

496
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:48,780
My brother really didn't secretly block my letters

497
00:38:48,780 --> 00:38:51,459
or stop Lu Ping from coming to see me?

498
00:38:51,459 --> 00:38:55,439
The general was extremely worried about you so how could he secretly plot these things?

499
00:38:55,439 --> 00:38:57,800
Young Lord Lu never came at all.

500
00:38:57,800 --> 00:39:02,659
Miss was so badly hurt but he didn't even rush to visit.

501
00:39:02,659 --> 00:39:05,699
As I can see, he really has no conscience.

502
00:39:05,699 --> 00:39:07,920
What do you know?

503
00:39:07,920 --> 00:39:09,959
Go out! Leave me alone.

504
00:39:09,959 --> 00:39:11,840
Yes.

505
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:20,400
Little bandit, if you don't come to see me,

506
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:22,540
I also won't see you again, either.

507
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:25,100
Let's just make a clean break then!

508
00:39:59,620 --> 00:40:03,920
Darn it! He left so fast, his clothes left even faster.

509
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:06,419
He didn't leave even his shadow behind.

510
00:40:07,260 --> 00:40:10,199
- Whom are you scolding at?
- I'm scolding at you!

511
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,940
