512
00:40:27,940 --> 00:40:31,160
If I came any later, I wouldn't have been able to get it back.

513
00:40:33,520 --> 00:40:35,220
It hurts.

514
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:39,920
- Do you believe now? It's not a dream this time.
- What are you doing here?

515
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:41,820
The Big Dipper is going to hold a Seven Star Convention.

516
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:43,900
I'm here to deliver the Seven Star invitation.

517
00:40:44,890 --> 00:40:46,939
