518
00:40:46,939 --> 00:40:48,610
Really?

519
00:40:49,420 --> 00:40:52,159
You didn't walk through a perfectly good front entrance but climbed over a wall instead.

520
00:40:52,159 --> 00:40:55,780
- You really are a bandit.
- Aren't you usually quite smart?

521
00:40:55,780 --> 00:40:57,430
What's wrong with you today?

522
00:40:57,439 --> 00:41:02,100
You have so many questions but just couldn't get any answers.

523
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:06,180
I am just a bandit.

524
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:09,600
